Class FastHuffmanDecoder<Symbol>

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.kivakit.data.compression.codecs.huffman.FastHuffmanDecoder<Symbol>
public final class FastHuffmanDecoder<Symbol> extends Object
The method decode(ByteList, SymbolConsumer) decodes a string a byte at a time from the given ByteArray using a set of lookup tables built from a HuffmanCodec.
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
